    {
        "id": "bleakfalls_sanctum",
        "name": "Bleakfalls Barrow — Sanctum",
        "type": "dungeon",
        "region": "whiterun_hold",
        "description": "The inner sanctum of Bleakfalls Barrow. A massive sarcophagus dominates the chamber, inscribed with ancient dragon runes. A Word Wall towers behind it — ancient script carved into living rock, pulsing with faint blue light. Cold radiates from the sarcophagus. Something stirs within.",
        "detailedDescription": "You step into the heart of the barrow. The room is vast, carved from the mountain itself. Columns of ancient stone rise to a vaulted ceiling lost in shadow. Before you stands a Word Wall — a curved wall of dark stone covered in glowing dragonscript. The words seem to call to you. But first — the sarcophagus lid begins to slide. The Draugr Overlord awakens.",
